<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>
    <AbilityDef>
        <defName>reimucard</defName>
        <label>符卡宣言</label>
        <description>符卡系的技能初次使用时要进行宣言,在有效时间内再使用进行发动,虽然是一次性使用却是强力的必杀技。

进行符卡宣言时要有至少一层灵力(灵力通过满P注入),宣言后可以使用三种灵梦的强力符卡</description>
        <abilityClass>merissu.Ability_ReimuCard</abilityClass>
        <iconPath>Abilities/reimucard</iconPath>
        <cooldownTicksRange>300</cooldownTicksRange>
		<displayOrder>1</displayOrder>
        <aiCanUse>false</aiCanUse>
		<targetRequired>false</targetRequired>
		<casterMustBeCapableOfViolence>false</casterMustBeCapableOfViolence>
        <verbProperties>
            <verbClass>Verb_CastAbility</verbClass>
			<drawAimPie>false</drawAimPie>
			<requireLineOfSight>false</requireLineOfSight>
            <warmupTime>1</warmupTime>
            <soundCast>spell</soundCast>
			<targetable>false</targetable>
            <targetParams>
                <canTargetSelf>true</canTargetSelf>
            </targetParams>
        </verbProperties>
    </AbilityDef>

    <HediffDef>
        <defName>ReimuCardDeclared</defName>
        <label>符卡宣言</label>
        <defaultLabelColor>(255,0,0)</defaultLabelColor>
        <description>已进行符卡宣言,在音乐结束前释放符卡吧</description>
        <hediffClass>HediffWithComps</hediffClass>
        <isBad>false</isBad>
        <tendable>false</tendable>
		<maxSeverity>1.0</maxSeverity>
        <abilities>
			<li>DreamSeal</li>
			<li>Ability_YinYangFlyingBirdWell</li>
			<li>EightDragonSlayerArray</li>
		</abilities>
		<comps>
			<li Class="HediffCompProperties_SeverityPerDay">
				<severityPerDay>-24</severityPerDay>
				<showHoursToRecover>true</showHoursToRecover>
			</li>
            <li Class="merissu.HediffCompProperties_PlayMusicOnce">
                <songDef>reimu1</songDef>
            </li>
		</comps>
    </HediffDef>

    <AbilityDef>
		<defName>DreamHeavenly</defName>
		<label>「梦想天生」</label>
        <abilityClass>merissu.Ability_DreamHeavenly</abilityClass>
		<description>总之是究极奥义,发动时用大量的符纸包围对手将其压制,使出这张符卡的话,这场战斗对于对手来说就没有任何胜算了。

需要消耗五层灵力进行发动,威力极其恐怖,注意不要在室内使用</description>
		<iconPath>Abilities/MusouTensei</iconPath>
		<cooldownTicksRange>800</cooldownTicksRange>
		<displayOrder>200</displayOrder>
		<aiCanUse>true</aiCanUse>
		<targetRequired>false</targetRequired>
		<verbProperties>
			<verbClass>Verb_CastAbility</verbClass>
			<range>99</range>
			<warmupTime>0.5</warmupTime>
			<soundCast>DreamHeavenly</soundCast>
            <targetParams>
                <canTargetSelf>true</canTargetSelf>
            </targetParams>
		</verbProperties>
	</AbilityDef>

	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseBullet">
		<defName>DreamHeavenlyHakureiTalisman</defName>
		<label>博丽灵符</label>
		<thingClass>merissu.DanmakuBullet</thingClass>
		<graphicData>
			<texPath>Other/DreamHeavenlyHakureiTalisman</texPath>
			<drawSize>(0.8,0.8)</drawSize>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
		</graphicData>
		<projectile>
			<damageDef>hakurei</damageDef>
			<damageAmountBase>100</damageAmountBase>
			<alwaysFreeIntercept>true</alwaysFreeIntercept>
			<stoppingPower>1</stoppingPower>
			<speed>40</speed>
		</projectile>
	</ThingDef>

